{
  "stem": "2170.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the hospital, and they tried to help me everywhere they can.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They always brought in, I saw, all kind of children, little children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the hospital, actually, the building where the hospital was a theater.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Upstairs was the hospital and downstairs was-- was a regular theater going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were playing shows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yiddish shows with all Romanian actors and actresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my bed was by the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I used to look down on it because I heard the piano playing, and I always like music.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So at least I didn't have to think much about my pains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was also a once in awhile came in German, not SS, but from the German authorities to check on the hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they came in, I thought they came in to kill us all, but looked like that they did not have no authority to do that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I got better-- and I could-- I couldn't pick up my legs and my hands-- but later on when I got better and Dr.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Drobner, and Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Schwartz and Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Liul'kin, they would all go to me, and they were trying everything to do that I should survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I saw other children, I saw a little boy and a-- and a girl, the brother and sister, their father was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they brought them in very, very sick from another town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I saw they did not have nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So when I felt better, I run out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I got for them bread and milk and eggs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I stole it, and I brought it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They should have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they had very bad sickness.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
